[[File:Parvin Darabadi.jpg|thumb]] '''Parvin Darabadi''' ({{lang-az|Pərvin Darabadi}}; 1947 — 2017<ref>[https://books.google.ru/books?id=seE6DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA80&dq=парвин+дарабади+1947&hl=ru&sa=X&ved=0ahUKEwisqf-H6drYAhXoF5oKHULGAa4Q6AEILDAB#v=onepage&q=%D0%BF%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B2%D0%B8%D0%BD%20%D0%B4%D0%B0%D1%80%D0%B0%D0%B1%D0%B0%D0%B4%D0%B8%201947&f=false Historical Dictionary of Azerbaijan]</ref>) was a Doctor of Historical Sciences, professor at the [[International relations|International Relations]] Department, [[Baku State University]].
He is the author of more than 100 scientific, academic-methodological, and scientific-popular works on various problems of military-political history, geopolitics, and conflictology, including the following monographs:<ref>[http://www.worldcat.org/search?qt=worldcat_org_all&q=Parvin%20Darabadi Worldcat author listing ]</ref> * Voennye problemy politicheskoy istorii Azerbaidzhana nachala XX veka (Military Problems of Azerbaijan's [[Political history|Political History]] in the Early 20th century) (1991),<ref>OCLC 621236251</ref> * Geopoliticheskoe sopernichestvo v Kaspiiskom regione i Azerbaidzhan (Geopolitical Rivalry in the Caspian Region and Azerbaijan) (2001), * Geoistoria Kaspiiskogo regiona i geopolitika sovremennosti (Geohistory of the Caspian Region and Geopolitics of the Present Day) (2002),<ref>{{ISBN|978-5-8066-1526-9}}</ref> * Кавказ и Каспий в мировой истории и геополитике XXI века / Kavkaz i Kaspiĭ v mirovoĭ istorii i geopolitike XXI veka, (The Caucasus, and Caspian in world history and 21st century politics) (2010) <ref>{{ISBN|978-5-7777-0501-3}}</ref>
